text: Johan Elfvengren (born June 10, 1994) is a Finnish ice hockey player. He is currently playing with Lahti Pelicans in the Finnish Liiga. Elfvengren made his Liiga debut playing with Lahti Pelicans during the 2014–15 Liiga season.http://www.ess.fi/urheilu/itshockeytime/2015/01/23/pelicans- luisteluttaa-jaalle-kauden-yhdeksannen-kotimaisen-liiga-debytanttinsa ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish ice hockey forwards Category:Lahti Pelicans players
